--- error_log eval
[
    qr/\[notice\] .*? host "localhost" will resolve to "127\.0\.0\.1"/,
    qr/\[notice\] .*? host "localhost\.dev" will resolve to "127\.0\.0\.1"/,
    qr/\[notice\] .*? host "localhost2" will resolve to "127\.0\.0\.2"/,
